    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Prerequisite: Order of the Lycan</em></p><p>When your roll your saving throw against your Bloodlust, you can use your reaction to fail. When you fail in this way your unarmed strikes deal an additional number of damage dice equal to your Intelligence modifier (minimum of 1) and expand the critical strike range by 1 for each unarmed strike made in this way.<br /><br /><strong>Amplify</strong>. If more than one creature is equally near to you, and the random roll randomly to determine your target is an allied creature, you can reroll the random target select and choose either result. You can choose to amplify after you see the initial randomly determined target.</p>",
